4.3:
Mic 4:3 He shall judge between many peoples, and shall decide for strong nations afar off; and they shall beat
their swords into plowshares, and their spears into pruning hooks; nation shall not lift up sword against nation,
neither shall they learn war anymore;

4.13:
Mic 4:13 Arise and thresh, O daughter of Zion, for I will make your horn iron, and I will make your hoofs bronze;
you shall beat in pieces many peoples; and shall devote their gain to the LORD, their wealth to the Lord of the
whole earth.
